<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">
  <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light dark">
  <title>Suspicious: Submission Registered</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .full-width { width:100% !important; }
      .stack { display:block !important; width:100% !important; }
      .hide-mobile { display:none !important; max-height:0 !important; overflow:hidden !important; }
    }
    [data-ogsc] body { background-color: #EDF1F4; color: #333333; }
    [data-ogsb] .dark-section { background-color: #242a75; }
  </style>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#EDF1F4; width:100% !important; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%;" data-ogsc data-ogsb>
  <center style="width:100%; background-color:#EDF1F4;">
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table class="full-width" width="600" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="max-width:600px;">
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color:#242A75; padding:30px 20px 0 20px; text-align:center;">
                <img src="{{ company_logo }}" alt="{{ company_name }} logo" style="display:block; max-width:120px; width:100%; height:auto;">
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color:#242A75; padding:0 20px; text-align:center;">
                <img src="{{ acknowledge_bad_mail_logo }}" alt="Banner" style="display:block; width:100%; max-width:1600px; height:auto;">
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="dark-white-bg" style="background-color:#FFFFFF; padding:30px 20px; font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#333333; line-height:20px;">
                <div style="margin-bottom:16px;">
                  <span style="font-size:18px; color:#00BBDD;">Dear {{ recipient }},</span>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom:16px;">
                  Thank you for your submission to the {{ company_name }} team.
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom:16px;">
                  Unfortunately, your mail could not be processed because it was not sent in the correct format or was signed before submission.
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom:16px;">
                  <strong>To be analyzed, the suspicious mail must be sent as a full attachment (not forwarded).</strong><br>
                  Also verify you do <strong>not</strong> sign your mail before sending it to Suspicious.
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom:16px;">
                  In Outlook, you can:
                  <ul style="padding-left:20px; margin:8px 0 16px; list-style-type: disc;">
                    <li>Right-click on the mail and select “Forward as Attachment”</li>
                    <li>Or use <em>Ctrl + Alt + F</em> when the mail is selected</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="dark-section" style="background-color:#242A75; padding:30px 20px; font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#FFFFFF; line-height:20px;">
                <div style="margin-bottom:12px; font-style:italic;">
                  To see the definition of these conclusion terms, visit the cybersecurity glossary, <a href="{{ glossary }}" target="_blank" style="color:#FFFFFF; text-decoration:underline;">available here</a>. In case of questions, contact <a href="{{ inquiry }}" target="_blank" style="color:#FFFFFF; text-decoration:underline;">{{ inquiry_details }}</a>.
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom:12px; font-style:italic;">
                  You can also access the portal <a href="{{ company_online_portal }}" target="_blank" style="color:#FFFFFF; text-decoration:underline;">here</a> to view technical analysis.
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom:12px; font-style:italic;">
                  Your contribution to the Group security is fundamental to reinforce detection and response capabilities.
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom:12px; font-style:italic;">
                  With our kindest regards,
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color:#FFFFFF; text-align:center; padding:0 0 0 0;">
                <div style="background-color:#242A75; padding:10px 0; border-top:2px solid #FFFFFF; border-bottom:2px solid #FFFFFF;">
                  <strong style="font-size:15px; color:#FFFFFF; font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">{{ company_name }}</strong>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color:#242A75; text-align:center; padding:35px 20px; font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#FFFFFF;">
                <a href="{{ company_global_security_url }}" target="_blank" style="color:#FFFFFF; text-decoration:underline; font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px;">
                  {{ company_global_security_team }}
                </a>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td align="center" style="background-color:#242A75; padding:15px 0 20px 0;">
                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
                  <tr>
                    {% for company_social in company_socials %}
                    <td style="padding:0 5px;">
                      <a href="{{ company_social.url }}" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none; border:0;">
                        <img src="{{ company_social.logo }}" alt="{{ company_social.name }} icon" width="24" height="24" style="display:block; border:0;">
                      </a>
                    </td>
                    {% endfor %}
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </center>
</body>
</html>
